01:27:41.090 --> 01:27:43.480
who taught at Gelati
Monastery named Ioane Petritsi.

01:27:43.480 --> 01:27:46.000
In one of his writings,
he makes this analogy

01:27:46.000 --> 01:27:51.850
where the three voices
are like the Holy Trinity

01:27:51.850 --> 01:27:55.210
and how the three becomes one,
so we see the analogy, Dato says,

01:27:55.210 --> 01:27:58.510
in the chant where
three voices become one.

01:27:58.510 --> 01:28:01.190
[ Inaudible Comment ]

01:28:01.190 --> 01:28:05.680
