in his footsteps,

01:29:41.340 --> 01:29:44.920
follows his voice in the Caucuses.

01:29:44.920 --> 01:29:49.510
I believe that's what
the text is referring to.

01:29:49.510 --> 01:29:56.480
[ Foreign Language ]

01:29:56.480 --> 01:30:00.860
St. Nino continued the
work of Apostle Andrew.

